title: Should I Invest in Crypto? | Madison Malloy | St. Lucia Chairman's Reserve 1931
itunes:title: Should I Invest in Crypto? | Madison Malloy | St. Lucia Chairman's Reserve 1931
description: In the past few years, everybody's been talking about Crypto Currency. This week's guest talks  about that and cancel culture in the comedy world over rum. Madison Malloy is a TV producer, comedian and podcaster with a new book in the works. We taste rums from Haiti, Colorado and St. Lucia. Her favorite shouldn't surprise you.
